📄 Project Plan
Online Medication & Prescription Tracker
1. Project Title

Online Medication & Prescription Tracker

2. Problem Statement

In traditional healthcare systems, patients often face difficulties in managing their medications and remembering dosage schedules.
 Doctors also find it challenging to monitor patient adherence and update prescriptions efficiently.
  Manual processes for prescription handling and refill requests can lead to delays, errors, and poor communication between patients and healthcare providers.

Therefore, there is a need for a centralized digital system that can simplify medication tracking, improve prescription management, and enhance communication between patients, doctors, and administrators.

3. Project Description

The Online Medication & Prescription Tracker is a full-stack web application designed to help patients, doctors, and administrators manage medications and prescriptions digitally. 
The system improves medication adherence, simplifies prescription management, and enhances communication within the healthcare system.

4. Project Objectives

To develop a secure platform for managing prescriptions

To help patients track medication schedules and dosage

To enable doctors to monitor and update treatment plans

To automate refill request processes

To integrate AI chatbot support for user queries

5. Scope of the Project

The project includes:

User registration and authentication

Role-based access (Admin, Doctor, Patient)

Medication tracking system

Prescription management

Refill request handling

AI chatbot integration

The project does not include:

Real-time hospital system integration

Live pharmacy billing systems

